'''Zokor Polpot''' was [[Vice Chancellor (Coruscant University)|Vice Chancellor]] of the [[University of Coruscant/Legends|University of Coruscant]]. In an attempt to discredit his boss, Polpot stole the head of [[8t88/Legends|8t88]], chief [[Droid/Legends|droid]] administrator of the [[Woostri HoloScan Database]], during a [[Woostri/Legends|Woostri]] visit. The prank resulted in the chancellor's resignation, paving the way for Polpot to become UC head. [[Chancellor (University of Coruscant)|Chancellor]] Polpot later [[Death/Legends|died]] during a visit to [[Mawan/Legends|Mawan]], with 8t88 the suspected perpetrator.

